de_moonbase_alpha

This is the first release and has a few issues i want to address, also its a bit unknown as to how the map will behave when full of people so all feedback on lag, bugs and or ideas and suggestions are welcome and will be appreciated.....

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a bomb map and there are two bomb sites, one in one of the domes and the other can be found in the machine room...

Please remember that space is a vacum and the base is pressurised so check your fire around the windows...

The shutters at T spawn will come down at the start of the map and can be opened again after about 15 seconds (to stop the whole Team being wiped out at the start by someone who decides to shoot the windows)
